'''三角座'''是[[北天_(天球)|北天]]小[[星座|星座]]，原名“{{lang|en|Triangulum}}”源自[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]，意为“[[三角形|三角形]]”，指星座中最亮的三颗星组成狭长三角形。三角座为古巴比伦人和希腊人熟知，是公元二世纪天文学家[[克劳狄乌斯·托勒密|克劳狄乌斯·托勒密]]列出的48个星座之一。天体制图师[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]和[[約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德|約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德]]为星座恒星编目，并用[[拜耳命名法|拜耳命名法]]为其中六颗星命名。

[[天大将军九|天大将军九]]和[[天大将军十|天大将军十]]分别是3.0和4.0[[视星等|视星等]]的白色恒星，与3.41视星等的黄白色恒星[[婁宿增六|婁宿增六]]组成三角型。[[三角座ι|三角座ι]]是有名的双星系统，星系内还有三个[[恆星系統|恆星系統]]确知存在[[太陽系外行星|行星]]。三角座内包含多个星系，其中最亮且距地球最近的是[[三角座星系|三角座星系]]，又名[[梅西耶天體|梅西耶]]33，是[[本星系群|本星系群]]成员。此外，人类发现的第一个[[类星体|类星体]]{{lang|en|[[3C_48|3C 48]]}}也在三角座范围内。

== 历史和神话传说 ==
根据[[古巴比伦星表|古巴比伦星表]]，三角座与[[天大将军一|天大将军一]]共同组成名为“<sup>MUL</sup>APIN（{{cuneiform|𒀯𒀳|lang=sux}}）”（意为“犁”）的星座，这也是公元前一千年左右汇编的规范星表《[[纲要_(古巴比伦)|纲要]]》（{{lang|en|MUL.APIN}}）中呈现并命名的第一个星座。犁座是《纲要》“[[恩利尔|恩利尔]]之路”的第一个星座，位于太阳路径最北端，对应[[夏至|夏至]]前后45天。星座在二月黎明前的天上首次出现（[[偕日升|偕日升]]），代表[[美索不达米亚|美索不达米亚]]春耕开始的时间。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Rogers | first = John H. | title = Origins of the Ancient Constellations: I. The Mesopotamian Traditions | journal = Journal of the British Astronomical Association | volume = 108 | date = 1998 | pages = 9–28 | bibcode = 1998JBAA..108....9R}}</ref>

古希腊人把三角座称为“德尔托顿”（{{lang|gre|Δελτωτόν}}），因为星座形状看上去就像大写希腊字母[[Δ|Δ]]（念“德尔塔”）。经罗马作家音译，再[[拉丁语|拉丁化]]为“{{lang|en|Deltotum}}”（“德尔托顿”）<ref name="allen">{{cite book | last = Allen | first = Richard Hinckley | date = 1963 | origyear = 1899 | title = Star Names: Their Lore and Meaning | edition = Reprint | publisher = Dover Publications Inc. | location = New York, New York | isbn = 0-486-21079-0 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/starnamestheirlo00alle/page/414 414–415]}}</ref>。[[埃拉托斯特尼|埃拉托斯特尼]]把星座与[[尼罗河三角洲|尼罗河三角洲]]联系起来，罗马作家[[许癸努斯|许癸努斯]]则将星座与三角形的[[西西里岛|西西里岛]]关联，当时西西里岛就因形状人称“特里纳基亚岛”（{{lang|en|Trinacria}}，前面三个字母有三角之意）<ref name="ridpathtri">{{cite web | url = http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/triangulum.htm | title = Triangulum | author = Ian Ridpath | publisher = self-published | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2008-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080930180046/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/triangulum.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。罗马人认为，西西里岛守护女神[[刻瑞斯_(羅馬神話)|刻瑞斯]]曾恳求[[朱庇特|朱庇特]]把该岛置于天堂，所以又将三角座称为“西西里亚”（{{lang|en|Sicilia}}）<ref name="allen" />。包括[[喜帕恰斯|喜帕恰斯]]和托勒密在内的古希腊天文学家称星座“{{lang|gre|Τρίγωνον}}”（“三角座”），后来[[罗马化|罗马化]]成“{{lang|en|Trigonum}}”（“三角”）。其他名称如“{{lang|en|Tricuspis}}”（“三尖”）和“{{lang|en|Triquetrum}}”（“三角骨”）都源自星座形状。<ref name="allen" />[[婁宿增六|婁宿增六]]和[[天大将军九|天大将军九]]被称为“{{lang|ar|Al Mīzān}}”，在[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]中意为“刻度尺”<ref name="garfinckle1997">{{cite book | first1 = Robert A. | last1 = Garfinkle | title = Star-Hopping: Your Visa to Viewing the Universe | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, United Kingdom | date = 1997 | isbn = 0-521-59889-3 | page = 238 | url = https://books.google.co.in/books?id=40JzBYGREL0C&pg=PA238&redir_esc=y | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200912171345/https://books.google.co.in/books?id=40JzBYGREL0C&pg=PA238&redir_esc=y | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[中国天文学史|中国古天文学]]用[[天大将军|天大将军]]为三角座多颗恒星命名，指神话中的伟大将军，在[[占星术|占星术]]中代表荣誉<ref name="ridpathtri" /><ref>{{cite book | last = Olcott | first = William Tyler | date = 2004 | origyear = 1911 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/starloremythsleg0000olco/page/22 22]–23 | title = Star Lore: Myths, Legends, and Facts | url = https://archive.org/details/starloremythsleg0000olco | publisher = Courier Dover Publications | location = Mineola, New York | isbn = 978-0-486-43581-7}}</ref>。

17世纪德国天体制图师[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]将星座称为三分主星和三方世界（{{lang|la|Triplicitas and Orbis terrarum tripertitus}}），分别代表欧洲、亚洲和非洲三大区域。为与[[南天_(天球)|南天]]的[[南三角座|南三角座]]区别，星座还曾获名“北三角”（{{lang|la|Triangulus Septentrionalis}}）。<ref name="allen" />1690年，波兰天文学家[[約翰·赫維留|約翰·赫維留]]在《赫维留星图》（{{lang|la|''Firmamentum Sobiescianum''}}）中把[[三角座ι|三角座ι]]、[[胃宿增一|胃宿增一]]和[[胃宿增二|胃宿增二]]三颗光线黯淡的恒星单独分出，新组成[[小三角座|小三角座]]，原本的星座更名主三角座（{{lang|la|Triangulum Majus}}）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/triangulumminus.htm | title = Triangulum Minus | author = Ian Ridpath | publisher = self-published | accessdate = 2013-08-29 | archive-date = 2013-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054356/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/triangulumminus.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[國際天文聯會|國際天文聯會]]于20世纪20年代确立88个现代星座，三角座便是其一，没有认可赫維留划分的小三角座<ref name="garfinckle1997" />。

== 简介 ==
三角座的面积很小，北面和西面与[[仙女座|仙女座]]相邻，西接[[双鱼座|双鱼座]]，南挨[[白羊座|白羊座]]，东交[[英仙座|英仙座]]，星座中心位于天大将军一和[[娄宿三|娄宿三]]之间的中途位置<ref>{{cite book | last = Simpson | first = L. Phil | title = Guidebook to the Constellations: Telescopic Sights, Tales, and Myths | publisher = Springer | location = New York, New York | date = 2012 | page = 417 | isbn = 1-4419-6941-1 | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=7gde2t9ta4QC&pg=PA417&dq=delta+triangulum&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=delta%20triangulum&f=false | archive-date = 2020-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200912171344/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=7gde2t9ta4QC&pg=PA417&dq=delta+triangulum&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=delta%20triangulum&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1922年，国际天文联会确定以三字母缩写“{{lang|en|Tri}}”代指三角座<ref name="pa30_469">{{cite journal | last = Russell | first = Henry Norris | author-link = 亨利·诺利斯·罗素 | title = The New International Symbols for the Constellations | journal = [[通俗天文學_(美國雜誌)|Popular Astronomy]] | volume = 30 | pages = 469–471 | bibcode = 1922PA.....30..469R | date = 1922}}</ref>。1930年，[[尤金·德爾波特|尤金·德爾波特]]正式划分星座边界，形成拥有14条[[邊_(幾何)|边]]的多边形。根据[[赤道坐標系統|赤道坐標系統]]，星座[[赤经|赤经]]位于{{RA|01|31.3}}和{{RA|02|50.4}}之间，[[赤纬|赤纬]]位于25.60°到37.35°之间<ref name="boundary" />。三角座占据0.32%的夜空，约为132平方度，在88个星座中排名第78<ref name="bagnall">{{cite book | last = Bagnall | first = Philip M. | title = The Star Atlas Companion: What You Need to Know about the Constellations | publisher = Springer | location = New York, New York | date = 2012 | isbn = 978-1-4614-0830-7 | page = 436 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=KcIg02TKW6QC&pg=PA436&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200912171345/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=KcIg02TKW6QC&pg=PA436&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 显著特点 ==
{{see also|三角座恒星列表}}
拜尔将星座内五颗恒星编目，用[[拜耳命名法|拜耳命名法]]分配“{{lang|la|[[Α|Α]]}}”到“{{lang|la|[[Ε|Ε]]}}”五个希腊字母。[[約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德|約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德]]在拜尔的基础上增加“{{lang|la|[[Η|Η]]}}”、“{{lang|la|[[Ι|Ι]]}}”和四个[[拉丁字母|罗马字母]]，但大部分都在后世的星表和星图中淘汰，只有“{{lang|la|Ι}}”沿用至今<ref name="wagman">{{cite book | last = Wagman | first = Morton | date = 2003 | title = Lost Stars: Lost, Missing and Troublesome Stars from the Catalogues of Johannes Bayer, Nicholas Louis de Lacaille, John Flamsteed, and Sundry Others | publisher = The McDonald & Woodward Publishing Company | location = Blacksburg, Virginia | isbn = 978-0-939923-78-6 | pages = 301–302, 348}}</ref>。佛蘭斯蒂德用[[佛蘭斯蒂德命名法|佛蘭斯蒂德命名法]]为16颗恒星分配数字编号1到16，但他在星表上标以“1”的对应位置并不存在恒星，估计是坐标有误。英国天文学家[[弗朗西斯·贝利|弗朗西斯·贝利]]推测佛蘭斯蒂德错把坐标写成32<sup>[[赤经|s]]</sup>，实际所指的恒星应该是7.4[[视星等|视星等]]的{{lang|en|HD}} 10407。贝利还指出，[[白羊座VZ|三角座16]]距白羊座更近，所以将之归入白羊座。<ref name="wagman"/>

[[Image:TriangulumCC.jpg|thumb]]

=== 恒星 ===
三角座因三颗较为明亮的恒星组成狭长三角形得名，其中最亮的是3.00视星等的白[[巨星|巨星]]天大将军九<ref name="garfinckle1997" />，距地球127[[光年|光年]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Beta+trianguli&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = Beta Trianguli | work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2018-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180722213545/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Beta+trianguli&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | dead-url = no }}</ref>。天大将军九实际是[[聯星|分光双星]]，主星是光谱等级{{lang|en|A5IV}}的白星，质量达太阳的3.5倍，已经开始扩张并结束主序星生命周期。人类对另一颗星尚缺乏了解，经计算归入质量约为1.4倍太阳的[[黃-白矮星|黃-白矮星]]。两星围绕[[质心|共同的重心]]轨道旋转，公转周期31天，恒星周围50到400[[天文單位|天文單位]]范围还有[[岩屑盤|岩屑盤]]环绕。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Kennedy | first1 = G. M. | last2 = Wyatt | first2 = M. C. | last3 = Sibthorpe | first3 = B. | last4 = Phillips | first4 = N. M. | last5 = Matthews | first5 = B. | last6 = Greaves | first6 = J. S. | date = 2012 | title = Coplanar Circumbinary Debris Disks | journal = [[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 426 | issue = 3 | pages = 2115–2128 | bibcode = 2012MNRAS.426.2115K | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2012.21865.x | arxiv = 1208.1759}}</ref>

第二亮的星是3.41视星等的黄白[[次巨星|次巨星]]婁宿增六，同样属分光双星，位于[[娄宿三|娄宿三]]西北偏北方向约七度的天空，是三角形的顶点<ref name="motz">{{cite book | last1 = Motz | first1 = Lloyd | last2 = Nathanson | first2 = Carol | title = The Constellations: An Enthusiast's Guide to the Night Sky | publisher = Aurum Press | location = London, United Kingdom | date = 1991 | pages = 310–312 | isbn = 1-85410-088-2}}</ref>。[[A型主序星|白主序星]][[天大将军十|天大将军十]]是组成三角形的第三颗恒星，光谱等级{{lang|en|A1Vnn}}，视星等4.00，距地球约112光年<ref name="sb1">{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Gamma+Trianguli&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = Gamma Trianguli | work = [[SIMBAD|SIMBAD Astronomical Database]] | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809160453/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Gamma+Trianguli&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | dead-url = no }}</ref>。天大将军十的自转速度很快，大小约为太阳两倍，[[光度|光度]]约33倍，周围也像天大将军九一样由岩屑盤环绕，岩屑盘半径约为太阳到地球距离的80倍<ref name="apj660_2_1556">{{cite journal | last1 = Rhee | first1 = Joseph H. | last2 = Song | first2 = Inseok | last3 = Zuckerman | first3 = B. | last4 = McElwain | first4 = Michael | title = Characterization of Dusty Debris Disks: The IRAS and Hipparcos Catalogs | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 660 | issue = 2 | pages = 1556–1571 | date = 2007-05 | doi = 10.1086/509912 | bibcode = 2007ApJ...660.1556R | arxiv = astro-ph/0609555}}</ref>。[[天大将军十一|天大将军十一]]和三角座7都位于天大将军十附近，组成分光三星系统，其中天大将军十一还是分光双星，由两颗距地球35光年，尺寸接近太阳的[[G型主序星|黄主序星]]组成。两颗黄主序星相距仅0.1天文单位，以十天周期相互公转。<ref name="kalerdeltatri">{{cite web | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/deltatri.html | title = Delta Trianguli | last = Kaler | first = Jim | work = Stars | publisher = University of Illinois | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809134329/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/deltatri.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>天大将军十一是三角座距地球最近的恒星系统<ref name="bagnall" />，相比之下仅5.25视星等的三角座7就要远得多，距地球约280光年<ref>{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=7+Trianguli&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = 7 Trianguli | work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809143606/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=7+Trianguli&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[三角座ι|三角座ι]]也是双星系统，其中一颗发出强烈黄光，另一颗是对比鲜明的淡蓝色恒星，能通过中型望远镜区分，两颗恒星本身又都是内部距离很近的联星<ref>{{cite book | last = Burnham | first = Robert Jr. | date = 1978 | title = Burnham's Celestial Handbook | url = https://archive.org/details/burnhamscelestia02robe | publisher = Dover Publications | location = New York, New York | isbn = 0-486-24065-7 | accessdate = 2020-09-13}}</ref>。三角座{{lang|en|X}}属[[食雙星|食雙星]]系统，视星等以0.97天为周期在8.5到11.2范围变化<ref name="levy05">{{cite book | last = Levy | first = David H. | title = David Levy's Guide to Variable Stars | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, United Kingdom | date = 2005 | page = 227 | isbn = 0-521-60860-0 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=Df9d8FBagqEC&pg=PA227&dq=%22X+trianguli%22&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=%22X%20trianguli%22&f=false | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200913033517/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=Df9d8FBagqEC&pg=PA227&dq=%22X+trianguli%22&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=%22X%20trianguli%22&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。三角座{{lang|en|RW}}是[[激变变星|激变变星]]，距地球约1075光年，以[[白矮星|白矮星]]为主，另一颗是光谱等级{{lang|en|K7 V}}的[[橙矮星|橙主序星]]。白矮星从橙主序星不断汲取物质，形成显著的[[吸积盘|吸积盘]]。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Groot | first1 = Paul J. | last2 = Rutten | first2 = Rene G.M. | last3 = van Paradijs | first3 = Jan | date = 2004 | title = A Spectrophotometric Study of RW Trianguli | journal = Astronomy & Astrophysics | volume = 417 | pages = 283–291 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20031771 | arxiv = astro-ph/0401029 | bibcode = 2004A&A...417..283G}}</ref>

三角座{{lang|en|R}}是[[刍藁变星|长期刍藁变星]]，视星等以267天为周期在6.2至11.7范围变动<ref name="levy05" />，距地球约960光年，是光谱等级{{lang|en|M3.5-8e}}的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=R+Tri&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = R Trianguli – Variable Star of Mira Ceti type | work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809123449/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=R+Tri&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[三角座XX|三角座XX]]又名{{lang|en|HD}} 12545，是8.42视星等、光谱等级{{lang|en|K0III}}的橙巨星，距地球约520光年<ref name="sbxx">{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=HD+12545&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = XX Trianguli – Variable of RS CVn type | work = [[SIMBAD|SIMBAD Astronomical Database]] | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809121248/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=HD+12545&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1999年，天文学家利用[[多普勒成像|多普勒成像]]技术在三角座{{lang|en|XX}}表面发现直径超过太阳的巨大[[星斑|星斑]]<ref>{{cite journal | bibcode = 1999A&A...347..225S | title = Doppler imaging of stellar surface structure. XI. The super starspots on the K0 giant HD 12545: Larger than the entire Sun | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 347 | pages = 225 | last = Strassmeier | first = K. G | year = 1999}}</ref>。

人类已经在三角座发现两个[[恆星系統|恆星系統]]包含[[太陽系外行星|行星]]。{{lang|en|[[HD_9446|HD 9446]]}}是距地球约171光年的类太阳恒星，拥有两颗质量分别为0.7和1.8倍[[木星|木星]]的行星，公转周期分别是30和193天<ref name="aaa513">{{cite journal | display-authors = 6 | last1 = Hébrard | first1 = G. | last2 = Hébrard | first2 = G. | last3 = Bonfils | first3 = X. | last4 = Ségransan | first4 = D. | last5 = Moutou | first5 = C. | last6 = Delfosse | first6 = X. | last7 = Bouchy | first7 = F. | last8 = Boisse | first8 = I. | last9 = Arnold | first9 = L. | date = 2010 | title = The SOPHIE Search for Northern Extrasolar Planets: II. A Multi-planet System Around HD 9446 | journal = Astronomy & Astrophysics | volume = 513 | page = A69 | url = https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full_html/2010/05/aa13790-09/aa13790-09.html | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/200913790 | bibcode = 2010A&A...513A..69H | arxiv = 1001.0682 | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | archive-date = 2018-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181222211644/http://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full_html/2010/05/aa13790-09/aa13790-09.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[HD_13189|HD 13189]]}}是光谱等级{{lang|en|K2II}}的橙巨星，尺寸约为太阳的两到七倍，拥有的行星很可能是[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]，尺寸约为木星八到二十倍，公转周期472天。人类发现的所有带行星恒星中，{{lang|en|HD}} 13189属于尺寸较大的一员。<ref name=aaa437_2_743>{{cite journal | last1 = Hatzes | first1 = A. P. | last2 = Guenther | first2 = E. W. | last3 = Endl | first3 = M. | last4 = Cochran | first4 = W. D. | last5 = Döllinger | first5 = M. P. | last6 = Bedalov | first6 = A. | title = A giant planet around the massive giant star HD 13189 | journal = [[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | date = 2005 | volume = 437 | issue = 2 | pages = 743–751 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20052850 | bibcode = 2005A&A...437..743H | url = https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/pdf/2005/26/aa2850-05.pdf | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2017-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170814040744/https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/pdf/2005/26/aa2850-05.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 深空天体 ===
[[File:The_peculiar_asymmetry_of_NGC_949.jpg|thumb]]

意大利天文学家[[乔瓦尼·巴蒂斯特·霍迪尔纳|乔瓦尼·巴蒂斯特·霍迪尔纳]]（{{lang|it|Giovanni Battista Hodierna}}）早在十七世纪就发现[[三角座星系|三角座星系]]（又名[[梅西耶天体|梅西耶]]33），是非常遥远的[[本星系群|本星系群]]星系，距地球约230万光年，视星等达到5.8，在理想夜空下能用肉眼识别。但作为光线散射天体，如果夜空存在[[光害|光污染]]，那么即便借助小型或双筒望远镜也很难看到。三角座星系是直径4.6万光年的[[螺旋星系|螺旋星系]]，比[[仙女座星系|仙女座星系]]和[[银河系|银河系]]都小。星系距仙女座不到300[[秒差距|秒差距]]，所以有假说称三角座星系相当于仙女座星系的卫星系。<ref name="pawlowski">{{cite journal | last1 = Pawlowski | first1 = Marcel S. | last2 = Kroupa | first2 = Pavel | last3 = Jerjen | first3 = Helmut | date = 2013 | title = Dwarf Galaxy Planes: the Discovery of Symmetric Structures in the Local Group | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 435 | issue = 3 | pages = 1928 | arxiv = 1307.6210 | doi = 10.1093/mnras/stt1384 | bibcode = 2013MNRAS.435.1928P}}</ref>三角座星系在婁宿增六西北偏西方向3.5度，[[奎宿九|奎宿九]]西南方向7度，已经接近双鱼座边界<ref name="motz" />。星座内的{{lang|en|[[NGC_604|NGC 604]]}}是[[电离氢区|电离氢区]]，是恒星形成的所在<ref>{{Cite web | title = NGC 604: Giant Stellar Nursery in M33 | date = 1996-08-16 | access-date = 2020-09-13 | url = https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap960816.html | editor1-last = Nemiroff | editor1-first = R. | editor2-last = Bonnell | editor2-first = J. | work = [[每日一天文圖|Astronomy Picture of the Day]] | publisher = [[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]] | archive-date = 2019-06-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608173823/https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap960816.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
[[File:A_distorted_duo_IC_1727_UGC_1249.jpg|left]]

除三角座星系外，三角座还有多个12到14视星等的[[NGC天體表|NGC星系]]<ref name="garfinckle1997" />，其中最大的{{lang|en|[[NGC_925|NGC 925]]}}螺旋星系长十[[弧分|弧分]]，视星等12；接下来是11.6视星等的五弧分{{lang|en|[[NGC_672|NGC 672]]}}[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]。{{lang|en|NGC}} 672与{{lang|en|IC}} 1727相距仅8.8万光年，看起来存在互动，两者距地球1800万光年。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.noao.edu/outreach/aop/observers/n672.html | title = NGC 672 | last = Block | first = Adam | date = 2003-10-20 | publisher = National Optical Astronomy Observatory | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150524081149/http://www.noao.edu/outreach/aop/observers/n672.html | access-date = 2015-05-24 | archive-date = 2015-05-24 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>{{lang|en|NGC}} 672、{{lang|en|IC}} 1727，以及附近四个[[不规则星系|矮不规则星系]]共同组成{{lang|en|NGC}} 672星系群，观察结果表明六个星系在过去一千万年间都曾爆发恒星形成。估计星系群还与人称{{lang|en|NGC}} 784星系群的另外六个星系相连，该群以主棒旋星系{{lang|en|[[NGC_784|NGC 784]]}}命名。两个星系群加上另外两个孤立矮星系，共计十四个星系看起来都在朝同一方向移动，而且有可能都属[[暗物质|暗物质]][[大尺度纖維狀結構|大尺度纖維狀結構]]的组成部分。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Zitrin | first1 = Adi | last2 = Brosch | first2 = Noah | date = 2008 | title = The NGC 672 and 784 galaxy groups: evidence for galaxy formation and growth along a nearby dark matter filament | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 390 | issue = 1 | pages = 408–420 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2008.13786.x | arxiv = 0808.1789 | bibcode = 2008MNRAS.390..408Z}}</ref>三角座的{{lang|en|[[3C_48|3C 48]]}}是人类发现的第一个[[类星体|类星体]]，但起初并未确认它是类星体，所以1963年在[[室女座|室女座]]发现的{{lang|en|[[3C_273|3C 273]]}}才是人类辩识出来的第一个类星体<ref>{{cite book | last = Robertson | first = Peter | title = Beyond Southern Skies: Radio Astronomy and the Parkes Telescope | publisher = Cambridge University Press | location = Cambridge, United Kingdom | date = 1992 | page = 234 | isbn = 0-521-41408-3 | accessdate = 2020-09-13 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=OBOY2G_3BCgC&pg=PA234&dq=3C+48&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=3C%2048&f=false | archive-date = 2020-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200913062019/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=OBOY2G_3BCgC&pg=PA234&dq=3C+48&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=3C%2048&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。3{{lang|en|C}} 48亮度仅16.2视星等，位于婁宿增六西北方向约五度<ref name="motz" />。
{{clear}}

